<div class="pop_main">
##编辑模式
#if($editmode == '1')
<h2>调仓明细<em class="js-pop-close"></em></h2>
<form action="/main/investadv/editTransPlan" method="post" class="dc_detail_content">
	<input type="hidden" id="transidipt" name="transid" value="$!transinfo.transid">
	<input type="hidden" id="advidipt" name="advid" value="$!transinfo.advid">
	<input type="hidden" name="editmode" value="1">
	#if(!$errormsg)
        <div class="operations">
            <span class="new_add">新增</span>
            <span class="del">删除</span>
            <label class="shengxiao">是否生效：
                <select name="validflag" id="validflag">
                    <option value="1" #if($transinfo.state == '1') selected="selected" #end>是</option>
                    <option value="0" #if($transinfo.state == '0') selected="selected" #end>否</option>
                </select>
            </label>
        </div>
	#end
    <table class="item_table">
        <tbody>
        <tr class="table_head">
	        <th>选择</th>
            <th>基金类型</th>
            <th>基金代码</th>
            <th>基金名称</th>
            <th>调整方向</th>
            <th>旧资产占比</th>
            <th>可用资产占比</th>
            <th>新资产占比</th>
            <th>涉及金额</th>
        </tr>
        #if($transdetail && !$errormsg)
	        #foreach($instr in $transdetail)
		    #set($fundinfo = $fund_tool.getFundInfo($instr.fundcode))
            <tr>
	            <td><input type="checkbox" class="delchk" disabled="disabled"></td>
                <td>$!fundinfo.fundType.enumItemInfo</td>
                <td><input type="text" class="trandetail_fundcode curholds" name="fundCode" value="$!fundinfo.fundCode" readonly="readonly"></td>
                <td>$!fundinfo.fundName</td>
                <td><label class="opertext">$!enum_tool.getFofTransName($instr.opertype)</label><input type="hidden" name="operType" class="operType" value="$!instr.opertype"></td>
                <td>$!{number_tool.format('##.#%',$instr.originpercent)}</td>
                <td>$!{number_tool.format('##.#%',$instr.availpercent)}</td>
                <td><input type="text" name="newPercent" class="newPercent" value="$!{number_tool.format('##.#',$!{math_tool.mul($instr.newpercent, 100)})}">%</td>
                <td><input type="text" name="operBalance" class="operBalance" value="$!{number_tool.format('#,###.##',$instr.operbalance)}" readonly="readonly">元</td>
            </tr>
	        #end
	    #else
	        <tr><td colspan="8">$errormsg</td></tr>
        #end
        </tbody></table>
	#if(!$errormsg)
        <div class="bottom_btn">
            <input type="button" class="keep" value="保存">
            <span class="close editclose">关闭</span>
##            <a href="javascript:volid(0);" class="zhiling">模拟生成指令</a>
        </div>
	#end
</form>
#else ##只读模式
<h2>调仓明细<em class="js-pop-close"></em></h2>
<div class="dc_detail_content">
    <table class="item_table">
        <tbody>
        <tr class="table_head">
            <th>基金类型</th>
            <th>基金代码</th>
            <th>基金名称</th>
            <th>调整方向</th>
            <th>旧资产占比</th>
            <th>新资产占比</th>
            <th>涉及金额</th>
        </tr>
    #if($transdetail && !$errormsg)
	    #foreach($instruction in $transdetail)
		#set($fundinfo = $fund_tool.getFundInfo($instruction.fundcode))
        <tr>
            <td>$!fundinfo.fundType.enumItemInfo</td>
            <td>$!fundinfo.fundCode</td>
            <td>$!fundinfo.fundName</td>
            <td>$enum_tool.getFofTransName($instruction.opertype)</td>
            <td>$!{number_tool.format('##.#%',$instruction.originpercent)}</td>
            <td>$!{number_tool.format('##.#%',$instruction.newpercent)}</td>
            <td>$!{number_tool.format('#,###.##',$instruction.operbalance)}元</td>
        </tr>
	    #end
	#else
	    <tr><td colspan="7">$errormsg</td></tr>
    #end
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="bottom_btn">
        <span class="close">关闭</span>
    </div>
</div>
#end
<div class="zhuyi">
    <dl>
        <dt>注意：</dt>
        <dd>1. 基金代码和新资产占比可用手工修改，其他字段为只读字段。</dd>
        <dd>2. 通过新旧资产占比的关系，自动填写调整方向。</dd>
        <dd>3. 持仓中默认有钱袋子基金，且新资产占比不得小于0.4%。</dd>
        <dd>4. 只能删除旧资产占比为0的基金，新增的基金旧资产占比为0。</dd>
        <dd>5. 同一个T日内，只能有一个调仓方案生效。</dd>
        <dd>6. 可用资产占比是指当日可用于交易基金份额的对应资产比例。在卖出及减持的情况下，需要考虑份额是否可用。</dd>
    </dl>
</div>
</div>